        <mxCell id="flowDetail" parent="1" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=10;spacingLeft=4;" value="1️⃣   User opens HTTPS URL in browser&#xa;2️⃣   DNS resolves to CloudFront edge&#xa;3️⃣   CloudFront checks cache (HIT/MISS)&#xa;4️⃣   On MISS: fetches from S3 via OAC&#xa;5️⃣   S3 returns index.html&#xa;6️⃣   CloudFront caches &amp; serves to user&#xa;7️⃣   Browser runs game (JS canvas)&#xa;8️⃣   Score submitted → API → Lambda → DB" vertex="1">
